              </Glosses>
              <Comments>In {S:05800700900024} it may be important to indicate clearly that it was not Levi himself who received the tenth but his descendants. Therefore, one may render the latter part of {S:05800700900024} as ‘Levi, whose descendants collect the tenth, also paid it.’</Comments>
